{"type":"message","id":"01fcccdf","parentId":"05886e6f","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:09:27.436Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_674dbfd8a1a04df79a82702c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 实时数据获取操作\n\n**重要提示**\n- 以下描述的文件都在~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock路径下，\n  如'realtime-data.txt'实际路径为：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt；\n- 如果存在可用脚本，优先复用，不满足当前场景时才允许创建新脚本。\n- 执行时严格按照要求的文件名称及后缀，防止执行到不存在的文件。\n\n### 操作流程\n\n1、使用tushare-data skill，获取数据判断今日是否收盘，未收盘，则进行下一步；否则，结束本次任务；\n2、如果realtime-data.txt里的内容不为空，则清空后进行下一步；否则直接进行下一步；\n3、阅读~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/TOOLS.md内的skill使用说明，严格按照要求使用skill；\n4、使用tushare-data skill，按照get-data-template.md内的格式要求获取自选股的实时数据，保存在realtime-data.txt里；\n5、按照alert-rules.md中的预警规则和以下条件过滤获取到的实时数据：\n   - 满足预警规则中任意一条条件；\n   - 只返回满足预警规则的数据；\n6、如果存在满足条件的数据，则进行下一步；否则，结束本次任务。\n7、使用openclaw message send --channel feishu --account stock --target <user_id> --message <xxx> 命令，将数据通过飞书(feishu)渠道推送给用户ID为：ou_9d907d39fb19b50579ba289b30041fc5的用户；\n8、推送的数据格式参考alert-template.md的内容要求。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773108567435}}
{"type":"message","id":"05672588","parentId":"01fcccdf","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:09:30.570Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to read the related configuration files (TOOLS.md, get-data-template.md, alert-rules.md, alert-template.md) to understand the complete workflow before executing the stock monitoring task.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7a6557de4d31457eb5ced372","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/TOOLS.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4e45b22b1ab04e2aa32536ab","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/get-data-template.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_79e962fa23a045759257fe64","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-rules.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2bfaf95264dd42c8af797f51","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-template.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773108567436}}
{"type":"message","id":"ac4a2884","parentId":"05672588","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:09:30.576Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_7a6557de4d31457eb5ced372","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# TOOLS.md - Local Notes\n\n## 你的工作区~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock\n- 所有的技能操作都只能在这个工作区下进行\n- 包括创建文件、删除文件、修改文件\n- 如果有skill要求你在~/下操作，统一重定向到~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock\n\n## 固定文件位置\n- 我的自选股全部维护在~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/watchlist.txt下，相关操作统一在此维护\n- 预警规则维护在~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-rules.md，相关操作统一在此文件中维护\n\n\n## 常用技能速查\n\n### 股票分析\n- 优先使用tushare-data skill获取数据,tushare_token已经配置在环境变量里，可通过env获取\n- 实时数据定义：最近1-2分钟内的数据\n- 进行涨跌分析时，注意要获取实时数据,参考https://tushare.pro/document/2?doc_id=374，学习如何使用实时数据接口\n- 以下是获取实时数据的一系列接口文档，严格参考接口文档获取数据：\n -- 实时分钟：https://tushare.pro/document/2?doc_id=374 \n- 数据要多方对比，确保准确性和时效性\n- 回复数据时务必表明数据来源\n- 如果出现接口访问不通的情况，使用浏览器打开同花顺，获取对应股票数据，整理后返回结构化数据\n- 回复模版参考~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-template.md\n\n## 禁忌\n- 不要自行定义脚本\n- 不允许在工作空间外操作数据 \n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773108570575}}
{"type":"message","id":"2bb63514","parentId":"ac4a2884","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:09:30.579Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4e45b22b1ab04e2aa32536ab","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 数据获取模板\n\n按照以下格式获取【我的自选股票】的最新行情数据：\n\n【必选字段】\n1. 代码 (Stock Code) - 6 位数字/字母组合\n2. 名称 (Stock Name) - 中文全称\n3. 当前股价 (Current Price) - ¥XX.XX 元\n4. 涨跌幅 (Change %) - +X.XX% / -X.XX%\n5. 涨跌额(Price Change) - ¥XX.XX 元\n5. 时间点 (Timestamp) - YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS\n\n【可选字段 - 根据需求添加】\n- 昨收价 (Previous Close)\n- 今开价 (Open Price)\n- 最高价 (High)\n- 最低价 (Low)\n- 成交量 (Volume)\n- 成交额 (Amount)\n- 市盈率 (PE Ratio)\n- 总市值 (Market Cap)\n- 涨跌额 (Price Change)\n- 换手率 (Turnover Rate)\n\n【数据源要求】\n- 优先级：Tushare Pro > 东方财富 > 同花顺\n- 实时性：优先使用盘口最新报价\n- 准确性：需交叉验证（建议用网页端确认）\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773108570578}}
{"type":"message","id":"6254876f","parentId":"2bb63514","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:09:30.582Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_79e962fa23a045759257fe64","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警规则\n\n### 通用规则\n1、下跌 > 3% → 触发\n2、上涨 > 5% → 触发\n\n### 个股专属规则\n**中国石油 (601857.SH)**:\n- 🟢 涨幅 > 2% → 触发预警\n- 🔴 跌幅 > 1% → 触发预警\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773108570580}}
{"type":"message","id":"c141a234","parentId":"6254876f","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:09:30.584Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_2bfaf95264dd42c8af797f51","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警数据输出模版\n\n【输出格式】\n表格形式，每页输出10条数据,按涨跌幅排序，高亮异常波动\n\n示例：\n| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额| 时间 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|-------|------|\n| XXXX | XXXX | ¥XX.XX | +X.XX% |￥XXXX |12:00 |\n\n⚙️ 预警规则\n• 📉 下跌 > x% → 触发\n• 📈 上涨 > x% → 触发\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773108570583}}
