{"type":"message","id":"f0aaebdf","parentId":"79107d4c","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:09:42.030Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_dfa2d60dee80494eadda0e93","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import tushare as ts\n\n# 核心：替换成你自己的 tushare pro token\npro = ts.pro_api('d5dffac476638f230dbe209bef04cd97b100c2dd3ddd10ddf85bc33d')\n\n# 获取浦发银行600000.SH的1分钟实时数据\ntry:\n    df = pro.rt_min(ts_code='600000.SH', freq='1MIN')\n    \n    # 打印数据结果\n    print(\"=== 浦发银行1分钟实时数据 ===\")\n    print(df)\n    \n    # 可选：保存为CSV文件到当前目录\n    df.to_csv('spdb_min_data.csv', index=False)\n    print(\"\\n数据已保存为 spdb_min_data.csv（当前目录下）\")\n\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"\\n运行失败：{str(e)}\")\n    print(\"\\n常见问题：\")\n    print(\"1. token错误 → 检查tushare个人中心的接口TOKEN\")\n    print(\"2. 积分不足 → rt_min接口需要≥2000积分\")\n    print(\"3. 非交易时间 → 仅9:30-11:30/13:00-15:00有数据\")\n    print(\"4. 股票代码错误 → 浦发银行是600000.SH（不是60000.SH）\")\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773108582029}}
{"type":"message","id":"9f62a73d","parentId":"f0aaebdf","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:09:45.385Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to check if today is a trading day and whether the market is currently open before proceeding with the real-time data fetch.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4234adda151c437f87140e2f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock && python3 -c \"\nimport tushare as ts\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\npro = ts.pro_api('d5dffac476638f230dbe209bef04cd97b100c2dd3ddd10ddf85bc33d')\n\n# 获取交易日历\ntoday = datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\ncal = pro.trade_cal(exchange='SSE', start_date=today, end_date=today, is_open='1')\n\nif len(cal) > 0:\n    print('MARKET_OPEN')\nelse:\n    print('MARKET_CLOSED')\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773108582030}}
